Description: Small floating Pomodoro and countdown timer for Linux X11
 Tiny Pomodoro XFCE is a small floating GTK timer for Linux X11 desktops, including XFCE and GNOME on X11.
 It supports Pomodoro mode, countdown timer mode, notifications,
 dark mode, autostart, and optional shutdown scheduling.

